column2: SELECT TOP # g.l,  g.b,  s.z as redshift, g.u, g.err_u,  g.g,  g.err_g,  g.r,  g.err_r,  g.i,  g.err_i,  g.z,  g.err_z,  g.extinction_g,  g.extinction_r  FROM  Galaxy AS g  JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) n ON n.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE  g.petroR9#_i/g.petroR5#_i > #  and ((flags & #) = #) and s.z > #
